  <Contents>k__BackingField:
  - You've been <shake>selected</shake> for a <color=#A8D8EA><b>field evaluation.</b></color>
  - <wave>Two tracks. People on each.</wave> One lever. <shake><color=#FF4444><b>One
    train.</b></color></shake>
  - You may <color=#88FF88>move them.</color> You may <color=#FFD700>pull the lever.</color>
    You may do <color=#FF6B6B><b>nothing.</b></color>
  - <wiggle><color=#C0C0C0><i>The timer is not decorative.</i></color></wiggle>
